{
  "stem": "6719.8",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We arrived, and the villa was on the island where Al Capone was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So when I was sitting down sunning myself and the excursion boats came by, I just waved my hand.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they thought I was a gangster.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Who the hell knows?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had a ball down there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyhow, nice time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I got back into the office.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We waited two weeks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I had a friend who worked in the next office, Sy Siegel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And apparently he came in, and he said to me, he says how was your holiday?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I said, who are you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Ah, I'm always joking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Comes back again.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Who are you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So he phoned Claire.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Claire phoned my doctor-- our doctor, who was also a personal friend.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He sent me to a psychiatrist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he sent me to a clinic in Rosedale.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only the difference between the shock treatment that I got in England and the shock treatment I got in Canada was different because down there they just gave it to you, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Here they gave you an injection of phenol.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just like an anesthetic, you were out, so you woke up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I spent, I think, four weeks down there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no, the only thing-- I had shock treatment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the only thing that happened was that I lost my memory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I forgot all my phone numbers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I forgot words.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Until this day, there are certain words that I have on the tip of my tongue, but I can't get them out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For instance-- and that we worked this out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We worked this out in a way because, at that time, at Shopsky's we were looking at cryogenic, making up foods that have all the moisture taken out, OK.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
